{"tid":49242,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Today  冬至 come to eat dinner","createTime":"2016-12-21T14:31:37.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T14:41:26.000Z","uid":35751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"44df4ef6d68966b4ed880b3b0e095d843d977f19","tid":49242,"uid":35751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T14:31:37.000Z","msg":"話說 我有一嗰啊哥<br />\n佢前幾年去外國讀書溝咗一嗰外國妹<br />\n嗰外國妹唔係好識中文<br />\n咁今晚冬至，我老豆老母就叫我叫佢地過嚟食飯<br />\n一開始因為我揾唔到我啊哥，咁我咪揾佢女朋友<br />\n但係我英文又唔係好好 唔識冬至嘅英文<br />\n就同佢講<br />\nToday <span style=\"color: red;\">冬至</span> come to eat dinner<br />\n但係佢地啱啱先到，我啊哥就問我<br />\n做咩唔好叫佢過嚟食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  搞到要哄佢先肯嚟<br />\n我即刻嘅反應係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我嗰陣仲未知做過啲咩激親佢<br />\n後來先知 學好英文係好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac41822de23b6e6abe085be945028a73eeecea3e","tid":49242,"uid":65160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T14:36:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a1182c8da267cf546e166ea16e6fff6bbc3a2b5","tid":49242,"uid":18320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T14:36:37.000Z","msg":"屌你老母留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d826d102e6c9f6b4a85f1e1812d9f88631933d37","tid":49242,"uid":65160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T14:37:39.000Z","msg":"today dont cone to eat dinner"},{"pid":"c697a7d1d57e9702d3a6e13053dd67a4d3650276","tid":49242,"uid":65160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T14:38:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>today dont come to eat dinner</blockquote><br />\n<br />\ncome 自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"